description:
Metallica - Whiskey In The Jar (Uncut)Music Clip 1999 ak

Whiskey in the Jar is  from 1998's album Garage, Inc. It's a traditional Irish song arranged by Eric Bell, Brian Downey and Phil Lynott, with a length of 5:04. In this song, James plays the lead guitar, and Kirk does the rhythm guitar.

This song was released by many bands. Metallica covered the version released by Thin Lizzy in 1972 on a single. Metallica's version was recorded in Sep-Oct 1998 at The Plant Studios in Sausalito, CA.

Video

Metallica recorded a video for the song, directed by Jonas Åkerlund and filmed in November 1998 in Brooklyn, NY. The video premiere was in March 16, 1999.
